<%- include("partials/header") -%>

<section class="lightSection">
  <div>
    <h1 class="title">Explore Wellington</h1>

    <div class="mb-3">
      <div class="swingvasion-box">
        <div class="swingvasion-details">
          <div class="m-4">
            <p>
              Wellington is a vibrant, compact city full of character. Whether
              you're here for a weekend or extending your stay, there's plenty
              to explore - from scenic walks and unique attractions to
              exceptional food and a famous coffee culture.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="swingvasion-box">
        <div class="swingvasion-details">
          <div class="m-4">
            <h3 class="p-0 mt-4">Must-See Attractions</h3>
            <p>
              If you want to explore the Wellington region, our community has
              brainstormed some ideas for things to do while you are here:
            </p>

            <ul>
              <li>
                <a target="_blank" href="https://www.visitzealandia.com/">
                  Zealandia</a
                >
              </li>
              <li>
                <a
                  target="_blank"
                  href="https://www.wetaworkshop.com/tours/wellington"
                >
                  Wētā Workshops</a
                >
              </li>
              <li>
                <a target="_blank" href="https://www.tepapa.govt.nz/">
                  Te Papa</a
                >
              </li>
              <li>
                Take the
                <a target="_blank" href="https://www.wellingtoncablecar.co.nz/">
                  Cable Car</a
                >
                to the
                <a
                  target="_blank"
                  href="https://wellingtongardens.nz/our-gardens/wellington-botanic-garden-ki-paekaka/"
                >
                  Wellington Botanic Gardens</a
                >
              </li>
              <li>
                Take a walk up one of Wellington's hills to check out the view.
                <a
                  target="_blank"
                  href="https://wellington.govt.nz/recreation/outdoors/walks-and-walkways/across-the-city/mount-victoria-loop"
                >
                  Mount Victoria</a
                >
                and
                <a
                  target="_blank"
                  href="https://www.wellingtonnz.com/visit/trails/mount-kaukau-summit-khandallah-park-loop"
                >
                  Mount Kaukau</a
                >
                (for the more adventurous) are popular options.
              </li>
              <li>
                <a
                  target="_blank"
                  href="https://www.doc.govt.nz/parks-and-recreation/places-to-go/wellington-kapiti/places/matiu-somes-island/"
                >
                  Matiu/Somes Island</a
                >
              </li>
              <li>
                <a
                  target="_blank"
                  href="https://wellington.govt.nz/recreation/outdoors/walks-and-walkways/beyond-the-city/red-rocks-coastal-walk"
                >
                  Red Rocks Coastal Walks</a
                >
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="swingvasion-box">
        <div class="swingvasion-details">
          <div class="m-4">
            <h3 class="p-0 mt-4">Food & Coffee</h3>
            <p>
              Wellington is known for its thriving food and coffee culture. The
              city centre is packed with excellent cafés, restaurants, and great
              eats. Don't miss trying a few of the city's standout cafés for
              exceptional coffee.
            </p>
              <ul>
              <li>
                <a target="_blank" href="https://frankscoffee.nz/">
                  Frank's Coffee</a
                >
              </li>
               <li>
                <a
                  target="_blank"
                  href="https://www.blackcoffeenewtown.com/"
                >
                 Black Coffee</a
                >
              </li>
              <li>
                <a
                  target="_blank"
                  href="https://baobab.co.nz/"
                >
                  Baobab Cafe</a
                >
              </li>
              <li>
                <a target="_blank" href="https://belenplantbakery.com/">
                  Belén Plant Bakery</a
                >
              </li>
              <li>
                <a target="_blank" href="https://www.pourandtwist.com/">
                 Pour and Twist</a
                >
              </li>
              <li>
                <a
                  target="_blank"
                  href="https://www.instagram.com/volcodoughclub/?hl=en"
                >
                Volco</a
                >
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="swingvasion-box">
        <div class="swingvasion-details">
          <div class="m-4">
            <h3 class="p-0 mt-4">Nature & Day Trips</h3>
            <p>
              If you have a car, there are some stunning places just outside
              Wellington worth exploring:
            </p>

            <ul>
              <li>
                <a
                  target="_blank"
                  href="https://www.wellingtonnz.com/visit/trails/escarpment-track"
                >
                  Paekākāriki Escarpment</a
                >
              </li>
              <li>
                <a
                  target="_blank"
                  href="https://www.martinborough-village.co.nz/wine-olives/"
                >
                  Martinborough Wineries</a
                >
              </li>
              <li>
                <a
                  target="_blank"
                  href="https://www.gw.govt.nz/parks/belmont-regional-park/"
                >
                  Belmont Regional Park</a
                >
                (We recommend starting at the Oakleigh st entrance)
              </li>
              <li>
                <a
                  target="_blank"
                  href="https://www.doc.govt.nz/parks-and-recreation/places-to-go/wairarapa/places/putangirua-pinnacles-scenic-reserve/"
                >
                  Putangirua Pinnacles
                </a>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="swingvasion-box">
        <div class="swingvasion-details">
          <div class="m-4">
            <h3 class="p-0 mt-4">Explore More</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>
                <a href="/travel-itineraries">Extend Your Trip</a> - Suggested
                itineraries to explore New Zealand and combine Southern Lights
                Swing and Swingvasion into one amazing adventure
              </li>
              <li>
                <a href="/getting-to-wellington">Getting Here</a> - Travel
                logistics and local transport
              </li>
            </ul>

            <p class="p-0 mt-4">Official Tourism Resources:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>
                <strong>New Zealand Tourism:</strong>
                <a target="_blank" href="https://www.newzealand.com/nz/">
                  www.newzealand.com</a
                >
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Wellington Tourism:</strong>
                <a target="_blank" href="https://www.wellingtonnz.com/">
                  www.wellingtonnz.com
                </a>
              </li>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%- include("partials/footer") -%>
